{"tid":291570,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"聰明既人其實好難搵到另一半","createTime":"2017-06-20T16:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T18:14:11.000Z","uid":24589,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b31ea2a4b32d7f37591d291fc1a5fb7924b5ecd2","tid":291570,"uid":24589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:09:41.000Z","msg":"同女友讀緊大學同一科，<br />\n我對呢科好有天份，可以輕鬆咁first hon，<br />\n而佢就好勤力 但成績都係普普通通咁<br />\n咁就出事啦，<br />\n係我心目中 佢絕對係聰明既人 可以入到呢一科已經係全港top2%，<br />\n而我自己band3出身， 更加見盡d垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢心目中只會不停覺得自己好蠢<br />\n每次問我題目之後都會喊一大輪<br />\n喊自己點解比唔上人地<br />\n其實我應該點樣做先可以令佢有返自信<br />\n定係根本我既存在會令到另一半好自卑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1800e601b8a5ef78c18b4bfb589acce9b7d6d7a4","tid":291570,"uid":11837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"咩科，同埋點解band3入到神科？"},{"pid":"fee00f4d337dbf0ecec4edd3864c5b14478734c5","tid":291570,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:13:16.000Z","msg":"成日喊嘅女人好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2cdf6a1fc151161acddd6bbfaf42e209cef8e1b","tid":291570,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:14:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩考完dse英文就讀大學？"},{"pid":"0f2984201c987750b0ec55d7eb3f35cbde5dbe3a","tid":291570,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:16:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩科，同埋點解band3入到神科？</blockquote><br />\n好出奇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見過個fd band3夠分讀神科都唔揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd945a659bbb2b18ce1c939d6c9774bb1debe1a","tid":291570,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"樓主精算<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor