":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:52:17.000Z","msg":"等放榜果排成日見樓主d post,咁就5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08968faaab4d2db1df6598356749be2096009b64","tid":291570,"uid":24589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ff<br />\n<br />\nband3入神科 ff<br />\n<br />\n算<br />\n<br />\n當真<br />\n<br />\n輕鬆first hon ff<br />\n<br />\n結論 樓主死全家 咪係到獻世</blockquote><br />\n入到自己有天份既科咁有咩問題<br />\n我英文差 12dse得level4<br />\n每人都有佢自己既專長<br />\n而家個問題係我搞唔掂另一半因為自己讀書呢方面比唔上人 就自卑到要喊<br />\n我想問下我有咩可以做<br />\n始終佢冇經歷過我band3時期難捱既日子"},{"pid":"3e5d0c73623147b71a1e585e1f3865f958a75135","tid":291570,"uid":24589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等放榜果排成日見樓主d post,咁就5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGrad左啦 5年改變左好多野<br />\n包括搵到自己定位 知道自己既專長<br />\n比絲打飛左都從跌低中成長過<br />\n巴打你又過成點"},{"pid":"0f858c9aa09028754e0995f14e967686b526f6f8","tid":291570,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T17:40:46.000Z","msg":"#1話讀緊，依家又話grad左，九唔搭八"},{"pid":"0ad459458c290d6d606482f7dd4bb6029dc4f4dc","tid":291570,"uid":111402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T18:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩科，同埋點解band3入到神科？</blockquote><br />\n好出奇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見過個fd band3夠分讀神科都唔揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好出奇<br />\n只係依位樓主神人 能人所不能 <br />\n如果用全港幾年數既BAND3學生計<br />\nBAND3入神科分分鍾係萬中無一<br />\n利申定 中學讀band3 既band3 頭5年入U既(計埋非8大) 10個唔夠 英文每年全級得單位數字有3OR ABOVE 未試過有人拎超過4</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n10個唔夠? 我果間已經有5個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 band3"}]}